title: Emerald Fennell & Carey Mulligan

description:
Emerald Fennell [The Crown, Call the Midwife, The Danish Girl] and Carey Mulligan [Drive, Shame, The Great Gatsby, An Education] join Anna to talk about their new movie Promising Young Woman, playing empowering and/or despicable characters, The Crown, answering dumb questions on a press tour, being blonde and more. Later in the episode Anna is joined again by psychotherapist, New York Times bestselling author, advice columnist and co-host of the Dear Therapist podcast, Lori Gottlieb who offers some expert advice to listeners.

Learn more about Lori Gottlieb at LoriGottlieb.com or by following her on Twitter @LoriGottlieb1 and Instagram @lorigottlieb_author.
